The NaN check should iterate ALL dictionary entries. A single NaN value in a JSON payload can cause `JSONEncoder` to throw or produce invalid JSON that breaks the analytics pipeline.

The clean exit flag pattern works by setting a UserDefaults flag to `true` on clean exit. On next launch, if the flag is `false`, the previous session crashed:

